def has_cup_near_milk(cup:item):
    # Function to check if a cup is near the milk
    symbol cup_near_milk=exists milk:item: is_milk(milk) and close(cup, milk)
    return cup_near_milk

    body:
        achieve close_char(char, milk)
        # Move character close to the milk
        achieve close_char(char, stove)
        # Move character close to the stove
        achieve is_on(stove)
        # Turn on the stove to heat up the milk
        achieve is_off(stove)
        # Turn off the stove after heating up the milk
